    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Paintings of scenes or decorations on a support, usually an object, made of porcelain, which is an impermeable translucent ceramic material. Mineral pigments blended in a medium are used to create the paintings, and the work is fired multiple times. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
